## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a6a4b-102">一旦建立執行緒時，就至少其中一種<xref:System.Threading.ThreadState>狀態，直到它所終止。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a6a4b-102">Once a thread is created, it is in at least one of the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadState> states until it terminates.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a6a4b-103">`ThreadStateException` 無法執行要求的操作，因為執行緒的目前狀態的方法會擲回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a6a4b-103">`ThreadStateException` is thrown by methods that cannot perform the requested operation due to the current state of a thread.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a6a4b-104">例如，嘗試重新啟動已中止的執行緒，藉由呼叫<xref:System.Threading.Thread.Start%2A>已終止則會擲回的執行緒上<xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a6a4b-104">For example, trying to restart an aborted thread by calling <xref:System.Threading.Thread.Start%2A> on a thread that has terminated throws a <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a6a4b-105"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException> 會使用 HRESULT COR_E_THREADSTATE，0x80131520 的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a6a4b-105"><xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException> uses the HRESULT COR_E_THREADSTATE, which has the value 0x80131520.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a6a4b-106">如需執行個體的初始屬性值的清單<xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>，請參閱<xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException.%23ctor%2A>建構函式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a6a4b-106">For a list of initial property values for an instance of <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException>, see the <xref:System.Threading.ThreadStateException.%23ctor%2A> constructors.</span></span>  
  
   
  
